212
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:07,604
Tio, Ramon?

213
00:14:10,057 --> 00:14:13,263
Crianças, levem-me
para casa.

214
00:14:17,273 --> 00:14:19,374
Então isto,
é tudo o que somos.

215
00:14:19,375 --> 00:14:20,978
Comida.

216
00:14:20,979 --> 00:14:24,607
E pensar que passamos a vida toda
sem saber a verdade.

217
00:14:24,639 --> 00:14:27,380
Adeus mundo criel!

218
00:14:31,389 --> 00:14:32,877
Erik.

219
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,681
Boadiceia.

220
00:14:36,343 --> 00:14:37,989
Aticcus.

221
00:14:45,692 --> 00:14:47,506
Ramon.

222
